--- title: "Cotação do ouro - Parte 4 " subtitle: "Neural Network Time Series Forecasting" author: "Pedro Lima" date: "2023-08-05" categories: [Série-Temporal,R,Machine Learning, Deep Learning] toc: true toc-depth: 3 draft: true --- ::: {.cell} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_a76af237a2ee277a9fa1f2bb8a0cf36e'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-3_da42cf6586779db4fc129bf9135930a1'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-4_68c026b0397be5b5a71b2622050402d3'} ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-5_7b6ea7d841062cd9687c466263828414'} ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-6_1dc9cff096645084a55b09e2b96b9b42'} ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ## Modelos ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-7_0a03ea6f7ef17f0174bcbc89d95cf9d5'} ```{.r .cell-code} nnet_model_auto <- nnetar_reg() %>% set_engine("nnetar") %>% fit(media ~ mes, data = training(splits)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-8_65af99134c524ba09892c1d7c7bf8d7c'} ```{.r .cell-code} nnet_model_adj <- nnetar_reg( seasonal_period = 12, non_seasonal_ar = 1, seasonal_ar = 1, hidden_units = 10, num_networks = 20, epochs = 500, penalty = 0 ) %>% set_engine("nnetar") %>% fit(media ~ mes, data = training(splits)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-9_b9e5769b5c3a6b65b0a4e1bf6cfdb3b3'} ```{.r .cell-code} nnet_model_nreg <- nnetar_reg() %>% set_engine("nnetar") %>% fit(media ~ mes + factor(month(mes, label = TRUE),ordered = FALSE), data = training(splits)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-10_7e4ae550fdc4e9eb7fe05b7d8d64b906'} ```{.r .cell-code} nnet_model_mreg <- nnetar_reg( seasonal_period = 12, non_seasonal_ar = 1, seasonal_ar = 1, hidden_units = 10, num_networks = 20, epochs = 500, penalty = 0) %>% set_engine("nnetar") %>% fit(media ~ mes+ factor(month(mes, label = TRUE),ordered = FALSE), data = training(splits)) ``` ::: ## Comparando os modelos ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-11_753b7a2e5e6e7a62321cb672cfee9713'} ```{.r .cell-code} model_table <- modeltime_table( nnet_model_auto, nnet_model_adj, nnet_model_mreg, nnet_model_nreg ) ``` ::: ## Calibrando ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-12_b75366c7a7330123e37357feabd0218b'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table <- model_table %>% modeltime_calibrate(testing(splits)) ``` ::: ## Residual ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-13_c3a10c01482f8ae4b5bf79e1309eecbd'} ```{.r .cell-code} # calib_table %>% # modeltime_residuals() %>% # plot_modeltime_residuals( # .type = "seasonality", # .interactive = FALSE # ) ``` ::: ## Accuracy ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-14_f7614a1f35d2a7faa6eaee8fd6e37508'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table %>% modeltime_accuracy() ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # A tibble: 4 × 9 .model_id .model_desc .type mae mape mase smape rmse rsq 1 1 NNAR(1,1,10)[12] Test 9.83 5.49 2.16 5.69 11.3 0.547 2 2 NNAR(1,1,10)[12] Test 8.96 5.03 1.97 5.18 10.5 0.300 3 3 NNAR(1,1,10)[12] Test 15.8 8.97 3.47 9.67 21.7 0.00115 4 4 NNAR(1,1,10)[12] Test 10.5 5.93 2.31 6.03 13.6 0.104 ``` ::: ::: ## Test set visualization ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-15_644b3f1a79ec2dbb183907fcd38e2bd7'} ```{.r .cell-code} calib_table %>% modeltime_forecast( new_data = testing(splits), actual_data = gold_mean ) %>% plot_modeltime_forecast() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ## Validação Cruzada ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-16_257d643eae6a10a79967dcabb27ef690'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted <- model_table %>% modeltime_fit_resamples( resamples = cv, control = control_resamples(verbose = FALSE) ) resamples_fitted ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # Modeltime Table # A tibble: 4 × 4 .model_id .model .model_desc .resample_results 1 1 NNAR(1,1,10)[12] 2 2 NNAR(1,1,10)[12] 3 3 NNAR(1,1,10)[12] 4 4 NNAR(1,1,10)[12] ``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-17_94e6fe3a8deb54257b760d365c5e39a1'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted %>% plot_modeltime_resamples( .point_size = 3, .point_alpha = 0.8, .interactive = FALSE ) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-17-1.png){width=1440} ::: ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-18_d11360c61c6716f19fe9608660f97cac'} ```{.r .cell-code} resamples_fitted %>% modeltime_resample_accuracy(summary_fns = mean) %>% table_modeltime_accuracy(.interactive = FALSE) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}

``` ::: ::: ## Forecast future ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-19_17495263b7bb9d4fbbfa4886ea1bc840'} ```{.r .cell-code} future_forecast_tbl <- calib_table %>% modeltime_refit(gold_mean) %>% modeltime_forecast( h = "1 year", actual_data = gold_mean ) ``` ::: ::: {.cell hash='index_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-20_809f60008b7b5ba67e9771825e739683'} ```{.r .cell-code} future_forecast_tbl %>% plot_modeltime_forecast() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
